                      <br />
                      </a>If you do not have the college credits necessary to meet the minimum requirement and are not enrolled in a college or university, we recommend clicking the links below to find information and resources that will assist you in acquiring the college credits needed to become one of New York's Finest. Also, it is important to understand all of your options when it comes to paying college tuition and expenses. Many of these sites can help you get the latest information about college costs, scholarships, financial aid applications, education loans, and college financing.<br />
